
---------------------
Requirement:
---------------------

The most important requirement are the shared lib of Monkey's Audio Codec, Audacious 3.4.x and headers.


--------------------
Compile:
--------------------
$ ./autogen.sh
$ ./configure
$ make

-------------------
Install
------------------

$ make install

PLAY APE FILES:

You need to restart your audacious media player when you finished the installation, so it can reload
the input plugins.


It is really easy, huh? Enjoy it!

